TITLE: Cypress Element Query Test
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to find and verify the presence of content on a page using cy.contains() command.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cypress-io/cypress-documentation/blob/main/docs/app/end-to-end-testing/writing-your-first-end-to-end-test.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
describe('My First Test', () => {
  it('finds the content "type"', () => {
    cy.visit('https://example.cypress.io')

    cy.contains('type')
  })
})
```

