TITLE: Making Assertions in Cypress
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to make assertions after clicking an element. It visits a page, clicks an element, and then asserts that the URL has changed as expected using cy.url().should().
SOURCE: https://github.com/cypress-io/cypress-documentation/blob/main/docs/app/end-to-end-testing/writing-your-first-end-to-end-test.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
