SOURCE: https://github.com/cypress-io/cypress-documentation/blob/main/docs/app/references/assertions.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
```
<input type="text" data-testid="example-input" disabled />
```

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
cy.get('[data-testid="example-input"]')
  .should('be.disabled')
  // let's enable this element from the test
  .invoke('prop', 'disabled', false)

cy.get('[data-testid="example-input"]')
  // we can use "enabled" assertion
  .should('be.enabled')
  // or negate the "disabled" assertion
  .and('not.be.disabled')
```

