TITLE: Window Before Load Event Handling
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to modify the window object before page load across all page transitions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cypress-io/cypress-documentation/blob/main/docs/api/cypress-api/catalog-of-events.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: javascript
